lead_paragraph: Washington's NFL pre-season game at Tampa Bay has been moved to Wednesday from Thursday due to the threat of severe weather, the Buccaneers said.

headline.print_headline: Bucs Move Pre-Season Game to Wednesday Due to Storm Threat
